  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to identify risks for work-related stress, stress reactions and
      long-term consequences among nurses, physicians, medical-technical and medical-therapeutic
      professions in Switzerland and to reduce those factors by an educational intervention for the
      supervisors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
